      "content": "thanks for those! plano and cary sound interesting. i'm curious though, when you say \"high-achieving\" or \"safe\" in those areas, are there certain neighborhoods or specific types of communities i should look for to make sure i'm avoiding areas that might be less stable or have more issues? like, are there certain demographics or vibes i should be aware of to ensure we get that stable environment we're looking for?",
